[6]	F. Reyes, René; Blanco, Gustavo; Lagarrigue, Andrés; Rojas, “Ley de bosque nativo: Desafíos Socioculturales para su Implementación,” 2016.
[7]	G. Kissinger, M. Herold, and V. De Sy, “Drivers of Deforestation and Forest Degradation,” A Synth. Rep. REDD+ Policymakers, p. 48, 2012.
